messages.title: 5 THINGS TO REMEMBER
messages.content: You don't need your polling card to vote. Polls are open 7am â€“ 10pm. If you've got a postal vote, but haven't sent it back yet, you can take it to your polling station before 10pm. If you don't know where your polling station is or you need a lift to vote, call our campaign hotline on 07912 699 314. Place a X next to your Labour candidate.

leaflet.additionalNotes: This election is a once-in-a-generation chance to transform our country and deliver the real change Rochester & Strood needs.
